  • ????????:
    ParameterNameDiscoverer

    public class DefaultParameterNameDiscoverer
extends PrioritizedParameterNameDiscoverer
    Default implementation of the ParameterNameDiscoverer strategy interface, using the Java 8 standard reflection mechanism (if available), and falling back to the ASM-based LocalVariableTableParameterNameDiscoverer for checking debug information in the class file.

    If Kotlin is present, KotlinReflectionParameterNameDiscoverer is added first in the list and used for Kotlin classes and interfaces.

    Further discoverers may be added through PrioritizedParameterNameDiscoverer.addDiscoverer(ParameterNameDiscoverer).
